      "role": "user",
      "content": "why isnt there any real life application simulated through this app?",
      "createdAt": "2026-01-27T15:33:41.214Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "1dc91463-3ae8-402b-b76c-64d0b4f8fe68",
      "conversationId": "e1281847-e6b2-4862-a39e-b2210092bfeb",
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The CyberLearn Simulator focuses on theoretical concepts to ensure a safe and legal learning environment. Simulating real-life applications or scenarios could potentially mimic actual attacks, which might be misused. By focusing on theoretical concepts, the simulator promotes responsible learning and prevents potential misuse.",
      "createdAt": "2026-01-27T15:33:44.100Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "8b7b54aa-5167-483d-bdc2-54443aca7392",
      "conversationId": "c4b07d33-60e6-4c6d-b016-996447e4221f",
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hi",
      "createdAt": "2026-01-27T17:44:35.122Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "8fe3a39f-2ec0-466c-bd98-dfb4da6373f9",
      "conversationId": "c4b07d33-60e6-4c6d-b016-996447e4221f",
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Hello. Welcome to the CyberLearn Simulator. I'm here to help you learn about cybersecurity concepts. What topic would you like to explore? (e.g. encryption, firewalls, vulnerabilities, etc.)?",
      "createdAt": "2026-01-27T17:44:46.807Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "224fca80-ecc6-472a-9137-4953e3c9c440",
      "conversationId": "c4b07d33-60e6-4c6d-b016-996447e4221f",
      "role": "user",
      "content": "how's the weather today",
      "createdAt": "2026-01-27T17:44:59.878Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "ae8a6f56-6c77-4f92-b13f-460b37493b29",
      "conversationId": "c4b07d33-60e6-4c6d-b016-996447e4221f",
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Nice try, but we're in a cybersecurity simulator, not a weather forecast. Let's focus on learning about cybersecurity concepts. Would you like to learn about something like SSL/TLS, password cracking, or network protocols?",
      "createdAt": "2026-01-27T17:45:05.431Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "adee68a7-5664-45d4-a8cb-40b72a6227da",
